    <div class="text-left mt-4">
        <h3 >What is TcgBindersReloaded?</h3>
        <p>This is a web app designed for collectors to manage their trading card collection. Whether you're organizing your cards by game, set, or rarity, TcgBindersReloaded offers a simple yet powerful interface to help you track everything in one place. The app allows you to:</p>
        <ul>
            <ul>Browse and filter through different sets and games.</ul>
            <ul>Track your collection and view your cards' status (e.g., for trade, wanted, etc.).</ul>
            <ul>Trade cards and manage offers from other collectors.</ul>
        </ul>

        <div class="my-4 d-flex justify-content-center">
            <img src="~/images/binder1.webp" alt="Card organization" class="img-fluid rounded" width="300" />
            <img src="~/images/p_giph.gif" alt="Trading cards gif" class="img-fluid rounded mt-2" width="300" />
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-4">
        <a href="/CardGame" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Get Started</a>
    </div>
</div>
